# **Nomenclature**

- $C_a$  Tip relief,  $\mu$ m;
- $d_a$  Tip diameter, mm;
- $d_f$  Root diameter, mm;
- $d_{Na}$  Active tip diameter, mm;
- $F_{bt}$  (Nominal) Transverse load in the plane of action (base tangent plane), N;
- $f_{\varepsilon}$  Load distribution influence factor;
- $h^*$  Tool addendum factor;
- $h_{Fe}$  Bending moment lever arm for tooth root stress relevant to load application at the outer point of single pair tooth contact, mm;
- *h*\* Tool dedendum factor;
- $K_A$  Application factor;
- $m_n$  Normal module, mm;
- N<sub>L</sub> Number of load cycles;
- $q_t$  Material allowance for finish machining, mm;
- $\hat{S}_F$  Safety factor against tooth root breakage;
- $s_{Fn}$  Tooth root chord at the critical section, mm;
- $x^*$  Profile shift factor;
- $Y_F$  Form factor;
- $Y_{\beta}$  Helix angle factor;
- $z_0$  Number of teeth of the tool;
- $\alpha_{\it Fen}$  Load direction angle, relevant to direction of application of load at the outer point of single pair tooth contact of virtual spur gears, °;
- $\alpha_n$  Normal pressure angle, °;
- $\alpha_{n0}$  Tool normal pressure angle, °;
- $\alpha_{pr0}$  Tool protuberance angle, °;
- $\beta_b$  Base helix angle, °;
- $\varepsilon_{\alpha}$  Transverse contact ratio;
- $\varepsilon_{\alpha n}$  Virtual contact ratio of the virtual spur gear;
- $\varepsilon_{\beta}$  Overlap ratio;
- $\theta_{oil}$  Oil temperature, °C;
- $\rho^*$  Tool tip radius factor;
- $\rho_{a0}$  Tool tip radius, mm;
- $\rho_F$  Tooth root radius at the critical section, mm;
- 1 Index for pinion;
- 2 Index for gear wheel;
- a Center distance, mm;
- b Face width, mm;
- d Reference cylinder diameter, mm;
- LOA Line of action;
  - *n* Rotational speed, min<sup>-1;</sup>
  - $pr_0$  Protuberance of the tool, mm;
    - r Relative change of the safety factor against tooth root breakage (2006/2019);
    - T Torque, Nm;
  - *u* Teeth ratio;
  - z Number of teeth;
  - $\beta$  Reference helix angle, °.
